.SH NAME
guix \- manual page for guix import (GNU Guix) 1.5.0rc1.47-fc2f5a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B guix
\fI\,import IMPORTER ARGS \/\fR...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run IMPORTER with ARGS.
.PP
IMPORTER must be one of the importers listed below:
.IP
composer
cpan
cran
crate
egg
elm
elpa
gem
gnu
go
hackage
hexpm
json
luanti
minetest
npm\-binary
nuget
opam
pypi
stackage
texlive
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
display this help and exit
.TP
\fB\-i\fR, \fB\-\-insert\fR=\fI\,FILE\/\fR
insert packages into FILE alphabetically
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
display version information and exit
